\c 3
\s Munyengetero waHabhakuki
\p
\v 1 Munyengetero waHabhakuki muporofita paShigionoti.
\p
\v 2 Haiwa, Jehovha, ndakanzwa shoko renyu, ndakatya; haiwa, Jehovha, basa renyu pakati pemakore, rimutsiridzei; pakati pemakore, zivisai pakutsamwa murangarire nyasha.
\v 3 Mwari wakabva kuTemani, Mutsvene kubva pagomo reParani. Sera. Matenga akafukidzwa neukuru hwake, nenyika yakazara nerumbidzo yake.
\v 4 Kupenya kwaiva kwakaita sechiedza, miseve yaibuda muruoko rwake, uye ipapo paiva nekuvanda kwesimba rake.
\v 5 Pamberi pake pakafamba hosha, nemurazvo unopfuta wakabuda patsoka dzake.
\v 6 Wakamira, ndokuyera nyika; ndokuiona, ndokudederesa marudzi, nemakomo ekusingaperi akapararira, zvikomo zvekare zvakakotama, nzira dzekusingaperi ndedzake.
\v 7 Ndakaona matende eKushani pasi penhamo; maketeni enyika yeMidhiani anodedera.
\p
\v 8 Jehovha wakatsamwira nzizi here? Hasha dzenyu dzairwisa nzizi here? Kutsamwa kwenyu kwairwisa gungwa here, zvamotasva mabhiza enyu, ngoro dzenyu dzoruponeso?
\v 9 Uta hwenyu hwakafukurwa kwazvo; shamhu dzakapikirwa neshoko renyu. Makaparura nyika nenzizi.
\v 10 Makomo akakuonai akatya, kudira kwemvura kwakapfuura; pakadzika pakabudisa izwi rapo, pakasimudzira maoko apo kumusoro.
\v 11 Zuva nomwedzi zvakamira paugaro hwazvo, zvichiona chiedza chemiseve yenyu ichipfuura, zvichiona kupenya kwepfumo renyu rinobwinya.
\v 12 Makatsika nyika makatsamwa, makapura ndudzi mune hasha.
\v 13 Makabuda kuzoponesa vanhu venyu, kuzoponesa muzodziwa wenyu; makakuvadza musoro weimba yowakaipa, muchifukura nheyo kusvikira kumutsipa wayo.
\v 14 Makabvovora misoro yavarwi vake namapfumo ake; vakauya sechamupupuri kundiparadza; kufara kwavo kwakaita sokwavanopedza varombo pakavanda.
\v 15 Makatsika gungwa namabhiza enyu, iwo murwi wemvura zhinji.
\v 16 Ndakanzwa, muviri wangu ukadedera, miromo yangu yakadedera ndichinzwa izwi; kuora kwakapinda mumapfupa angu, ndikadedera pandakange ndiri, nokuti ndinofanira kumirira zuva renjodzi ndinyerere, kana iye, anozorwa navanhu, achivawira.
\p
\v 17 Nokuti kunyange muonde ukasatunga maruva, nemizambiringa ikashaiwa zvibereko, kunyange kubereka komuorivhi kukakona, neminda ikasabereka zvokudya; kunyange makwai akapera muchirugu, nemombe dzikashaikwa mumatanga,
\v 18 kunyange zvakadaro ndichafara kwazvo muna Jehovha, ndichava nomufaro muna Mwari woruponeso rwangu.
\v 19 Jehovha Ishe isimba rangu, anoita tsoka dzangu dzive setsoka dzehadzi yenondo, anondifambisa pamatunhu angu akakwirira. Kumutungamiriri wekuimba, nemitengeranwa yangu.